{"tid":1027752,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"會用連坐法嘅教蓄係咩心態？","createTime":"2019-02-19T04:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T07:32:23.000Z","uid":191633,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e92be670ed0fd40e246fe25725a20840293b73ca","tid":1027752,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"新年執屋 摷到好多中學時嘅野 有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先利申 89年出世 讀男校<br />\n唔知而家仲有無老師係咁教學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nf2個年個班主任<br />\n為咗懲罰嗰幾個成日欠功課嘅同學<br />\n只要嗰幾條友一欠功課<br />\n坐佢地前後左右打斜嗰八個同學都要一齊處分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個月欠夠五次就留堂 欠夠十次就一個小過<br />\n搞到人心惶惶咁（雖然而家諗返起 覺得小過大過呢啲好閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但嗰時細個真係會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n我就坐正喺其中一條成日欠交嘅on9仔後面<br />\n成日好撚驚佢欠功課<br />\n為咗佢交齊 我地幾個仲會集體俾佢抄功課<br />\n條友就爽皮 無一份功課係要自己做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰時我係英文科長 有次佢連嗰本功課簿都無帶 又已經欠咗四次 幾個同學嘈話放學又要琴又要游水又要乜乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唯有向個老師講個大話&nbsp;話已經收齊啲簿<br />\n趁lunch嗰時買咗本新簿俾佢叫佢抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再攝返入疊簿入面&nbsp;放上功課架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本有啲人就係爛泥扶唔上柄<br />\n搞到全村人陪罰都唔會交功課架啦<br />\n何況上到high form都開始無乜人交功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔明佢咁罰晒全村人會有乜作為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54466909af6e684b0d5c61223cc43013eaf65165","tid":1027752,"uid":56111,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"連坐法根本就係搞分化<br />\n加劇校園欺凌<br />\n都唔撚明點解會有人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961c1596237d75f02a8efc7b558c6a1d81afde71","tid":1027752,"uid":191633,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"54466909af6e684b0d5c61223cc43013eaf65165","tid":1027752,"uid":56111,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"連坐法根本就係搞分化<br />\n加劇校園欺凌<br />\n都唔撚明點解會有人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"搞到唔應該受罰嘅人受罰<br />\n要受罰嗰個就受多一重欺凌 過街老鼠咁"},{"pid":"dbd98c3a80e1baf4bd63a118031af7600d0b663f","tid":1027752,"uid":2757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"咁點解為人師表嗰條撚屌唔鳩駛罰？"},{"pid":"36cfe54c61f3bb929d717dee7a2060d48850e6f1","tid":1027752,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd98c3a80e1baf4bd63a118031af7600d0b663f","tid":1027752,"uid":2757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"咁點解為人師表嗰條撚屌唔鳩駛罰？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係佢教到班人唔做功課打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec547257123fb69a7ce1f6206dc041c7ba287c06","tid":1027752,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:51:25.000Z","msg":"一齊罰呢啲係團隊運動先應該有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同班真係唔需要咁團結，好快就會畢業走人"},{"pid":"503ebc680749da28af39e4c185562c75cc2476fa","tid":1027752,"uid":191633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"最慘係有幾個同學嘅座位係食正兩個唔交功課嘅人隔離<br />\n佢地真係俾人記咗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個教畜真係講得出做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ac04dd814c6b85867dd18d8b7defe38d4a1211","tid":1027752,"uid":6222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:57:02.000Z","msg":"搞到軍訓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地做錯野無交功課關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"5ec2eed19336de4185bca622